::DarkMouse::

She stood behind Scorponok. She watched Megatron talk to Panzertron.  She 
took out a pocket scanner and saw only the three bots on the screen.  She 
put the scanner away. She stood there feeling a little out of place.  she 
wasn't in any kind of command position, yet Megatron had told her to join 
him on this meeting of his.  She wondered if she would end up being the 
sacrifial lamb as it were.  She just kept her eyes on Megatron and 
Panzertron.
